        {
            "_id": "Dwyi8KNK6wosK8vq",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Isolating Howl",
            "sort": 1100000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Rembles lets loose an unearthly howl filled with utter despair. All creatures other than barghests within a 60 foot emanation who hear the howl become filled with the sense that they're all alone in the world, and that an impossible distance spans between themselves and anything remotely connected to companionship. Affected creatures must attempt a @Check[will|dc:24] save with the following effects.</p>\n<p>Rembles can't use Isolating Howl again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Isolating Howl]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Convictions of loneliness fill the target's mind, and they cannot target allies or take the Aid action for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but the weight of being so alone crushes down on the creature, causing them to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 minute as well.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> There's no reason to try. The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed] from ennui and despair for 1 minute, but can attempt a @Check[will|dc:24] save at the end of each of their turns to break free from this despair—on a success, they're no longer paralyzed but become slowed 1 for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "auditory",
                        "emotion",
                        "incapacitation",
                        "mental",
                        "primal"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "wvm4r5nQM5hhQ41O",
