                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature damaged by the barghest's claws must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:24] save or be cursed. The cursed creature can't regain Hit Points except via magic until it returns to maximum Hit Points. The creature can attempt a new saving throw against the curse every 24 hours.</p>"
